Name: iceweather
Version: 0.1.1
Summary: Look up Icelandic weather information (observations, forecasts, etc.)
Home-page: https://github.com/sveinbjornt/iceweather
Author: Sveinbjorn Thordarson
Author-email: sveinbjorn@sveinbjorn.org
License: BSD
Description: # iceweather
        
        Python wrapper to look up Icelandic Met Office weather observations, forecasts, etc. Wrapper for the apis.is weather JSON API.
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```
        $ pip install iceweather
        ```
        
        ## Examples
        
        ## Version History
        
        0.1.1 - Fall back on other close weather stations for if err in result from closest station 
        0.1 - Initial release (10/09/2019)
        
